==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The moon and clouds of 8,000 [[里|li]].

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: bā qīan lĭ lù yún hé yùe

===Idiom===
'''[[八]][[千]][[里]][[路]][[云]][[和]][[月]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# Describes the great distances involved in a military campaign.
# To travel far and wide.

===Alternate forms===
[[八]][[千]][[里]][[路]][[雲]][[和]][[月]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

